{"tid":962670,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"2020年解讀港女全攻略","createTime":"2018-12-31T05:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T04:34:36.000Z","uid":150100,"like":77,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"446c6a32198a93d88b4ab32135d9e6cf5b8c1f79","tid":962670,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:03:29.000Z","msg":"事先聲明<br />\n由於依個攻略係屬於2020年，現在使用有機會出現無法預計嘅結果，本人並不會承擔任何責任。<br />\n<br />\n1. 個女仔喺whatsapp hea 覆<br />\n解讀：佢試探緊你係咪真係想同佢傾偈<br />\n做法：瘋狂whatsapp佢以顯示你嘅誠意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 個女仔同你講佢有男朋友<br />\n解讀：佢想你做佢男朋友<br />\n做法：直接拖佢隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 個女仔避開你對眼<br />\n解讀：佢覺得你對眼好吸引<br />\n做法：昅住佢，令佢產生愛意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4. 個女仔已讀不回<br />\n解讀：佢想同你傾電話<br />\n做法：打俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5. 個女仔拒絕你嘅表白<br />\n解讀：佢想你再嚟多次 (女仔中意被表白)<br />\n做法：嚟多幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n6. 個女仔唔肯同你做<br />\n解讀：佢想玩強姦遊戲<br />\n做法：強姦佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n7. 個女仔望住你笑<br />\n解讀：想含你條撚<br />\n做法：除褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n8. 個女仔向你表白<br />\n解讀：佢想同你扑野<br />\n做法：直接帶佢開房<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9. 個女仔block咗你<br />\n解讀：佢想引起你注意<br />\n做法：打電話俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n10. 個女仔成日偷望你<br />\n解讀：佢討厭你<br />\n做法：放棄佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以上都係基於樓主豐富嘅戀愛經驗<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">(失戀、苦戀、單戀)</span></span>所寫，絕對值得相信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310c4cee215c50588736a5b9b43145e5c41e4c42","tid":962670,"uid":116097,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:07:52.000Z","msg":"11. 個女仔話想同你分手<br />\n解讀：佢無聊屎忽痕<br />\n做法：大力屌佢屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f13b886802314b2e10a6663eafb47fa8ec4f35","tid":962670,"uid":150100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"310c4cee215c50588736a5b9b43145e5c41e4c42","tid":962670,"uid":116097,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:07:52.000Z","msg":"11. 個女仔話想同你分手<br />\n解讀：佢無聊屎忽痕<br />\n做法：大力屌佢屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:10:43.000Z","msg":"正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edcc49106ff11310aaf8f88d250f472797294ad9","tid":962670,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:12:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ca9be5d1e4e91d1d685614420864af50150ef801","tid":962670,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a7e5fe1659515b1420e3c44a8145c3f4cf4fe7","tid":962670,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:22:31.000Z","msg":"12. 係街有靚女經過<br />\n解讀：佢鐘意你<br />\n做法：就地正法 除褲抽插<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab4a2bf61d887c8f2783f0d7179973cb9777c1e","tid":962670,"uid":161190,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:26:50.000Z","msg":"睇咗樓主既攻略 而家d囡囡日日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但求樓主可以出飛女攻略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hk